Release checklist for duff
==========================

 * Make changes in the code
 * Comment all new symbols
 * Test the changes
 * Update NEWS
 * Update ChangeLog
 * Update HACKING
 * Update README
 * Update TODO
 * Update duff.1 (including date)
 * Build release file
 * Commit changes to CVS
 * Tag release in CVS
 * Upload release file to SF.net
 * Make release on SF.net
 * Update SF.net trove categorisation
 * Post SF.net news item
 * Post announcement to duff-devel
 * Make release on Freshmeat
 * Update project homepage
 * Update version number
 * Commit updated version number

